Vietnam's Prime Minister Pham Minh Trung attended the 3rd Vietnam National Digital Technology Enterprise Development Forum. Two main sessions were held during the 3rd Vietnam National Digital Technology Enterprise Development Forum. The discussion topics focused on digital technology enterprises and national digital transformation, digital technology enterprises and economic recovery and development during and after the COVID-19 epidemic.In 2021, the number of typical digital products in Vietnam has been cultivated, focusing on solving major problems facing Vietnam. Many digital products have been exported abroad, and Vietnam's digital technology ranking has risen. Minister Nguyen Manh Hung called on digital technology companies to take responsibility for developing national digital transformation platforms. At the forum, leaders of ministries and state agencies, enterprises, organizations and individuals who are researching, developing, applying and transferring digital technologies shared their breakthrough ideas and solutions to mobilize and pool social resources to develop Vietnam technology enterprises, work together to promote the country's digital transformation and economic recovery after the Chu Huy epidemic.It is an objective demand for development. Digital transformation has become a global issue. Digital transformation serves all people, so it needs to mobilize the participation of all people. People and enterprises are the core, main body, goal and driving force of digital transformation. Therefore, all policies need to be for people and enterprises. Premier Fan Mingzheng stressed that digital transformation needs to reflect the national spirit, with internal forces as the main, strategic, long-term and decisive factors, and external forces as the important and breakthrough point. He also believes that digital transformation needs to drive in-depth development and sustainable development, participate in the prevention and control of the new crown pneumonia epidemic, economic recovery and development, respond to subsequent changes, overcome the depletion of natural resources, and assist in green transformation and development of green energy. Digital transformation needs to participate in the protection and promotion of cultural values of relevant countries.Premier Fan Mingzheng asked governments, institutions and enterprises at all levels to strengthen leadership and guidance in the development of digital technology, improve understanding of digital transformation, and continue to formulate and improve the system on digital transformation.Strengthen national governance and promote the development of digital technology enterprises in a spirit of respect, communication, listening, positive and proactive. During the forum, Prime Minister Pham Minh Thang attended the award ceremony of the "Made in Vietnam" Excellent Digital Product Award 2021 and the opening ceremony of the "Made in Vietnam" Digital Product Exhibition.
